title: Add the location 18,142 to the Points of Interest
body:
> by 0xf39bf6c8b3f92f3acead822cb76b9fabc33b476f (Hearts)

## The Music Box

![The Music Box](https://api.decentraland.org/v1/parcels/18/142/map.png)

Should the scene located at 18,142 be added to the Point of Interest list?

## Description

Momma UFO came here straight out of the cosmos.  She's here to give out free Love in the form of light and musical vibrations.\
Designed by cyber-artist Miguelangelo Rosario.

**[Vote on this proposal on the Decentraland DAO](https://governance.decentraland.org/proposal/?id=a6be4ef0-e772-11eb-89c8-f9c6d1f05e5b)**
author: 0x5E23D08324f017d5425e59A2782C9ae27aCE0958
